Ranger Help for: make torch
============================

SYNTAX:      torch
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   2
BASE SP:     10
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to create a torch from harvested wood. The
torch provides light in dark areas, which is essential when exploring
caves, underground passages, or traveling at night. The Ranger must
have wood in their inventory to create the torch. How long the torch
lasts depends on the quality of the wood and the Ranger's crafting
skill.
